Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:20.52,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}kawaita kuuki furete mitara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:27.11,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}mebaeru hana no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:33.37,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}omoi no kakera afurete kuru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:46.05,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}kono te ni moraeta kimi no nukumori
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:55.06,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}takaramono ni naru mirai he michibiite kureta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:23:04.98,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}zutto kimi no koe wo oikaketeita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:10.49,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}itsu kara nan darou tsuyoku natta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:17.58,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}kiiroi sekai sagashita mono wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:25.29,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}tabiji no hate ni kitto mitsukaru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:14.39,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}Po mrazivé vichřici,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:20.52,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}v níž suchý vítr vál,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:27.11,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}se ve mně začínají vytvářet různé pocity,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:33.37,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}jako v květině, která brzy vykvete.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:46.05,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}Ve svých rukou stále cítím tvé teplo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:55.06,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}které mě vede k budoucnosti, jíž si mohu vážit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:23:04.98,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}Stále jdu za tvým hlasem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:10.49,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}a náhle jsme spolu zesílili.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:17.58,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}Na konci své cesty jistě najdeme,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:25.29,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}co hledali jsme v tomto světě.
